Name: Beautiful Beach Women's Standard Short-Sleeved T-Shirt 150g
Description:
Cool T-shirt it is suitable for summer, spring, fall and winter. It can be worn in family theme clothing, city streets, friends gathering, leisure and entertainment, travel, sports and fitness scenes.

[Design Note]:Front area printing

[Material Description]:100% cotton

[Product Performance]:Soft and comfortable hand feel, slightly elastic, good wearable and good fit, comfortable and fashionable, simple and practical, not easy to shrink, durable, fashionable and trendy.

[Applicable scenes]:Daily, home, travel, fitness sports, etc.

[Applicable crowd]:Ladies

[Special instructions]:This size data is measured under the clothes lay flat, due to different measurement methods, the error within 2-4cm is normal.
